      <title>德国经济显示出复苏迹象，但工业却举步维艰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-27/germany-recession-latest-economy-shows-signs-of-life-as-industry-struggles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过两年近乎于零的增长后，德国的经济前景正在向好。然而，消费者主导的复苏掩盖了工业持续疲软的局面，而且没有快速解决办法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-27/germany-recession-latest-economy-shows-signs-of-life-as-industry-struggles</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
